The Secret follower @lazymomdiaries shares with us about her thoughts on The Secret:⁠
"The Secret" is one of the best-selling self-help books by Rhonda Byrne. ⁠
What made it the best seller? ⁠
Is there is any magic trick to improve your life? ⁠
My answer is 'NO' there is no magic in this world that can change your life instantly but the magic lies within you, in your thoughts.⁠
And that secret is 'Positive Thinking'.⁠
DID YOU GET IT? ⁠
Let me explain a little more. ⁠
The law of attraction, which states that positive energy attracts positive things into your life, regulates your thinking and actions, and how you can use the power of positive thinking to achieve anything you can imagine.⁠
If you ever want to accomplish anything in your life, never doubt that you can't do it or you can't get it.⁠
Always firm in your belief, and stay positive, then things will start coming on your way by the will of nature.
